{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013766SpTbMY1uvg49iEtoJe","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"43e58b5f-4801-4d1c-b71e-1cb2980b19a0","uuid":"04755e70-1209-4e38-87ce-e1fd6d972f6a","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:29:44.291Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","oldString":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n\n### 14-4-observability-backend-choice","newString":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n\n### 16-3-update-proof-validation-for-tiers — create-story (2026-03-27T11:02Z)\n\nStory file already existed. Updated verification tags from `test-provable` to `cli-verifiable` format.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 10\n- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 5, Edit: 1, Glob: 3\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n\n### 16-3-update-proof-validation-for-tiers — dev (2026-03-27T11:05Z)\n\nNo issues reported. Clean implementation — 2 files changed, 9 new tests added.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 12\n- By tool: Read: 4, Edit: 5, Glob: 2, Grep: 1, Bash: 2\n- Files read: 5 unique, 6 total reads\n\n### 16-3-update-proof-validation-for-tiers — code-review (2026-03-27T11:09Z)\n\n**Bugs found:**\n- HIGH: Metrics zeroed when Docker enforcement skipped — downstream consumers see false zeroes. Fixed.\n- HIGH: `black-box` missing from LEGACY_TIER_MAP. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: Hardcoded tier names in regex (not derived from types.ts). Fixed with dynamic regex.\n- MEDIUM: No test for unrecognized tier value. Fixed.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 21\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 6, Edit: 5, Grep: 5, Glob: 4, Skill: 1\n\n### 16-3-update-proof-validation-for-tiers — verify (2026-03-27T11:24Z)\n\nALL_PASS (6/6 ACs). Unit-testable tier — no Docker needed. Build, tests (3887 pass), coverage 96.86%.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 13\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 3, Grep: 2, Write: 1\n\n### State corruption fix (2026-03-27T11:00Z)\n\nsprint-state.json had 4 stories (14-5, 14-6, 16-1, 16-2) reverted from `done` to `review` despite commits confirming them as done. Proof documents existed. Fixed by restoring `done` status. Root cause: likely ralph state reconciliation overwriting committed state between sessions.\n\n### 14-4-observability-backend-choice","originalFile":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n\n### 14-4-observability-backend-choice — verify (2026-03-27T08:20Z)\n\nTier A validation — proof existed with 10/10 PASS. Quick validation pass.\n\n### 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile — review (2026-03-27T08:25Z)\n\n**Bugs found:**\n- HIGH: Unsafe `as StackName` type cast in `dockerfile-generator.ts` masking type safety — FIXED\n- MEDIUM: Double `apt-get update` layer in Rust+Bevy Dockerfile output — FIXED\n- MEDIUM: Unquoted Python dist filename in COPY instruction (`env.ts:162`) — NOT FIXED\n\n**Tech debt:**\n- 14 stale `mockDetectStack` call sites in `verify-env.test.ts`\n- No logging when `getStackProvider()` returns undefined\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 20\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 10, Edit: 3, Grep: 5, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Files read: 13 unique, 14 total reads\n\n### 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile — code-review (2026-03-27T09:35Z)\n\n**Bugs found and fixed:**\n- HIGH: Subdirectory stack path not resolved before passing to provider — Bevy detection would silently fail for non-root stacks\n- MEDIUM: Missing DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive — apt installs could hang on interactive prompts\n- MEDIUM: Uncovered !provider and !section branches (66.66% branch coverage before fix)\n- MEDIUM: env.ts at 305 lines (extra blank line), over NFR1 300-line limit\n\n**Code quality issues NOT fixed (LOW):**\n- verify-env.test.ts still mocks dead detectStack import\n- Multi-stack Dockerfile creates redundant apt-get update per provider section\n- env.ts at 304 lines still over 300-line NFR1 limit\n- Story Dev Agent Record claims 12 generator tests but actual count was 9\n\n**Coverage:** 96.87% overall, all 157 files above 80% floor\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 24\n- By tool: Bash: 10, Read: 12, Edit: 6, Grep: 5, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Files read: 14 unique, 16 total reads\n\n### 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile — code-review-2 (2026-03-27T13:55Z)\n\nNo new bugs found. Previous HIGH/MEDIUM fixes verified solid. Coverage 97.45%, all files above 80% floor. 3856 tests passing. Status advanced to verifying.\n\n**LOW items not fixed:** fragile push() pattern in generator, no Docker syntax validation test, long line in env.ts.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 22\n- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 8, Grep: 4, Glob: 1, Skill: 0\n- Files read: 12 unique, 13 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile — verify (2026-03-27T14:00Z)\n\nALL_PASS (10/10 ACs). Unit-testable tier — no Docker needed. Build, tests, coverage all passed.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 24\n- By tool: Bash: 15, Read: 5, Grep: 4, Write: 2\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Second coverage run could have reused first output\n\n### 16-2-rewrite-parser-tier-classification — create-story (2026-03-27T14:15Z)\n\n**Problems:** Epic 16 has no dedicated epics file — definition comes from tech-spec-verification-tier-rework.md instead of standard epics document.\n**Workarounds:** Used tech spec as authoritative source for story definitions.\n**Risks:** 300-line limit for parser.ts is tight (278 lines, adding ~30 net).\n**Observations:** Story 16-1 already modified parser.ts to add working tier derivation; 16-2 is cleanup/simplification.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Read: 9, Grep: 2, Glob: 3, Bash: 1, Write: 1\n- Files read: 10 unique, 10 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 16-2-rewrite-parser-tier-classification — code-review (2026-03-27T10:40Z)\n\n**Bugs found:**\n- HIGH: `VERIFICATION_TAG_PATTERN` regex did not include `unit-testable` — backward compat silently broken. Fixed.\n- HIGH: `parseVerificationTag` used unsafe `as VerificationTier` cast without runtime validation. Fixed with guard.\n- MEDIUM: Missing test coverage for edge cases (empty string, unknown tags, unit-testable compat). 3 new tests added.\n\n**LOW not fixed:** Broad keywords risk false-positive classification. Keyword overlap between dimensions.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 9, Edit: 6, Grep: 2, Glob: 4, Skill: 1\n- Files read: 9 unique, 10 total reads\n\n### 16-2-rewrite-parser-tier-classification — verify (2026-03-27T10:50Z)\n\nALL_PASS (12/12 ACs). Unit-testable tier — no Docker needed. Build passed, 62 parser tests passing, parser-keywords.ts at 100% coverage. `codeharness verify` flagged `coverage_met` state flag (harness-level, not story-level). 5 test failures in unrelated modules (pre-existing).\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 4, Grep: 1, Write: 1\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: npm test run 3 times (could have been 1 with tee)\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":5,"newStart":1,"newLines":47,"lines":[" # Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27"," ","+### 16-3-update-proof-validation-for-tiers — create-story (2026-03-27T11:02Z)","+","+Story file already existed. Updated verification tags from `test-provable` to `cli-verifiable` format.","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: 10","+- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 5, Edit: 1, Glob: 3","+- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads","+","+### 16-3-update-proof-validation-for-tiers — dev (2026-03-27T11:05Z)","+","+No issues reported. Clean implementation — 2 files changed, 9 new tests added.","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: 12","+- By tool: Read: 4, Edit: 5, Glob: 2, Grep: 1, Bash: 2","+- Files read: 5 unique, 6 total reads","+","+### 16-3-update-proof